          <title>The 49ers bring back Robert Saleh for 2nd stint as defensive coordinator</title>
          <description><![CDATA[SANTA CLARA, Calif. (AP) — The San Francisco 49ers hired Robert Saleh for a second stint as defensive coordinator on Friday night after a failed tenure as head coach of the New York Jets. Saleh had been a candidate for head coaching jobs with Jacksonville, Dallas and Las Vegas.]]></description>
